reviewText: My grandson loves the Diego's adventures on DVD.
My daughter loves these videos. She is just 3 years old. We have about 20 of them. Can't say this is her favorite... but that might change tomorrow.
Excellent DVD for my grand daughter who loves Diego and Dora.  This is an excellent teaching tool that will be cherished for many years to come.
My granddaughter can put this cd in her dvd player and watch Diego anytime! Along with Dora it her favorite show on TV.
My twins love Diego. It is very difficult to find this video at such a great price. I ordered the video and within a week I had my product. No disappointments. Would order again from your company .

My son loves Diego.  He's only two, but he knows what he likes. I prefer Diego to Dora, Diego has more "bearable" plots.  I'm not certain if it's from Diego or not, but my son has been counting in the last couple of months.
Like all Diego videos, we appreciate the bilingual and eduacational aspect. My 3 yoa likes this one, but prefers others that have more songs in them.

Me and my son just love Diego!! This DVD comprises some of the collest animal-saving adventures ever to grace a TV set.

The only thing I wish it had where a few games included, or a poster of some kind (I know you can get to the web for the games, though). The price is just right.
Ever since my 3 year old grandson has had it in his hot little hands he has been watching it - he even thinks he can take it outside with him - great buy!!!!!!
Bought this for my niece and nephew whilst visiting them in USA. They loved it.  Fun to watch and things to learn whilst watching.
